WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:01.830
Ushbu o‘rganishlardan so‘ng biz

00:00:01.830 --> 00:00:05.620
ro‘yxat ko‘rinishidagi ro‘yxat elementiga 
bosish tinglovchisini qanday o‘rnatishni bilamiz.

00:00:05.620 --> 00:00:08.660
&gt;&gt; Biz o‘zimizning oynamizga qaytsak, 
bu yerda "ListView" ob’ekti bor bo‘lib, 

00:00:08.660 --> 00:00:10.540
unda bizning ro‘yxatimiz elementlari ko‘rinishi mavjud.

00:00:10.540 --> 00:00:13.600
Bunda biz "setOnItemClickListener" 
usuliga murojaat qilib, 

00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:15.106
tinglovchi ob’ektiga o‘tishimiz mumkin.

00:00:15.106 --> 00:00:19.970
&gt;&gt; Ushbu "ClickListener" 
ob’ektida "onItemClick" deb nomlangan 

00:00:19.970 --> 00:00:21.770
usul mavjud va unda biz 
istagan ko‘rsatmalar bo‘lishi mumkin.

00:00:21.770 --> 00:00:25.350
Masalan, tost xabari paydo bo‘lishi
yoki audio faylni ijro etish kabi narsalar. 

00:00:25.350 --> 00:00:27.020
&gt;&gt; Hop mayli.
Bu mantiqqa to‘g‘ri keladi.

00:00:27.020 --> 00:00:29.870
Va biz o‘rganuvchini kamroq 
ushlab turamiz, to‘g‘rimi?

00:00:29.870 --> 00:00:31.370
&gt;&gt; Lekin, men qo‘l ushlashni yaxshi ko‘raman.

00:00:31.370 --> 00:00:32.210
&gt;&gt; Jessica.

00:00:32.210 --> 00:00:32.860
&gt;&gt; Ha mayli. Hammasi joyida.

00:00:32.860 --> 00:00:36.010
Keyingi kodlash mashqlari bir 
nechta bosqichlarga ega bo‘lsa ham, 

00:00:36.010 --> 00:00:37.560
men o‘rganuvchilar uni yengib o‘tishga qodirligiga aminman.

00:00:37.560 --> 00:00:38.640
&gt;&gt; Qarang, bu insonni ruhlantiradi.

00:00:39.710 --> 00:00:42.080
&gt;&gt; Shunday qilib, keyingi vazifa uchun 
siz dasturni o‘zgartirishingizni xohlayman, 

00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:44.510
bunda ro‘yxat elementini 
bosganingizda audio fayl ijro etilishi kerak.

00:00:44.510 --> 00:00:45.910
&gt;&gt; Siz buni albatta qila olasiz.

00:00:45.910 --> 00:00:49.120
&gt;&gt; Avvalo, biz buni bitta 
audiofayl uchun amalga oshirishni boshlaymiz 

00:00:49.120 --> 00:00:53.390
va keyin har bir so‘z uchun 
to‘g‘ri audio fayllarni ijro ettirishga o‘tamiz.

00:00:53.390 --> 00:00:58.270
Shunday qilib, birinchi raqamli va barcha so‘z 
uchun bitta "luti" nomli audio faylni taqdim etmoqchiman.

00:00:58.270 --> 00:01:01.790
"MP3" faylini yuklab olish uchun 
test ostidagi yozuvlarni tekshiring 

00:01:01.790 --> 00:01:04.650
va hozirning o‘zida raqamlarning 
faolligini o‘zgartiring.

00:01:04.650 --> 00:01:06.480
Xo‘sh, siz ishni tugatganingizdan keyin
ilova qanday ko‘rinishga ega bo‘lishi lozim?

00:01:06.480 --> 00:01:10.438
Ro‘yxatdagi har qanday elementni bosganda, 
xuddi shu "lutti" so‘zini ijro etishi kerak.

00:01:10.438 --> 00:01:12.410
&gt;&gt; Lutti.

00:01:12.410 --> 00:01:15.200
&gt;&gt; Ushbu vazifani bajarganingizdan so‘ng 
oldinga siljing va ushbu katakchani belgilang.

